projects.description: ToDo List App is a kind of app that generally used to maintain our day-to-day tasks or list everything that we have to do, with the most important tasks at the top of the list, and the least important tasks at the bottom. It is helpful in planning our daily schedules

projects.title: 8-Queen Problem
projects.description:
Implemented a program in python to solve the 8 Queens Problem using a genetic algorithm. 
 The aim of the N-Queens Problem is to place N queens on an N x N board, in a way so that none of them can attack the other (means when any queen moves in directions vertical, 
 horizontal and diagonal no other queen found in the path)

projects.title: Bank Management System
projects.description:
Includes operations for Admin Panel, Staff Panel & ATM Services. To cater the suggestions/complains of Users we designed a complain-box as well. This was all done in Java Language with Swing Library for the UI.
Test data contained accounts of 5000 users with more than 100k records of transactions which were catered through Hash Tables to keep Big O close to O(1).
